@startuml use-case-diagram-part2
' Figure 2 of 2. Part 1: use-case-diagram.puml

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam titleFontSize 15
skinparam titleFontStyle bold
skinparam ArrowColor #2E5A88
skinparam usecaseBackgroundColor #E8F0FE
skinparam usecaseBorderColor #2E5A88
skinparam usecaseFontColor #102040
skinparam usecaseFontSize 11
skinparam actorFontSize 12
skinparam actorFontStyle bold
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FFF9E3
skinparam noteBorderColor #C9A227
skinparam noteFontSize 10
skinparam nodesep 60
skinparam ranksep 55

title Stock Guard - Use case diagram 2 of 2\nAnalytics, export, and system administration
left to right direction

actor "System\nAdministrator" as ADM
actor "Strategic (Business\nOwner and Stock\nAnalyst)" as ST

package "Analytics and administration" {
  usecase "View consumption\ntrends" as uA
  usecase "View reports and\nanalytics" as uB
  usecase "Export CSV / PDF" as uC
  usecase "Manage user\naccounts" as uD
  usecase "Configure system\nsettings" as uE
  usecase "Monitor health and\nserver logs" as uF
}

' Operational Staff does not access analytics/admin use cases in Part 2
' (Log usage and risk alerts are in Part 1)

ADM --> uB
ADM --> uC
ADM --> uD
ADM --> uE
ADM --> uF

ST  --> uA
ST  --> uB
ST  --> uC
ST  --> uF

note right of uA
  Only on **Strategic** role
  menu; not on System
  Administrator menu
  (``Sidebar``).
end note

@enduml